%% ODH Dashboard - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAuth as K8s API Server<br/>(SubjectAccessReview)
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant ModelRegUI as model-registry-ui<br/>8043/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant GenAIUI as gen-ai-ui<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTPS TLS

    Note over Browser,Dashboard: Flow 1: User Accesses Dashboard UI
    Browser->>Gateway: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS re-encrypt
    KRP->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA token
    K8sAuth-->>KRP: Allowed (projects list)
    KRP->>Dashboard: Forward (HTTP/8080, localhost)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User/Groups headers
    Dashboard-->>KRP: Static frontend assets
    KRP-->>Gateway: Response (HTTPS)
    Gateway-->>Browser: HTML/JS/CSS Response

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Frontend Makes K8s API Call
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/k8s/... (HTTPS/443)<br/>User token via kube-rbac-proxy
    Gateway->>KRP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRP->>Dashboard: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>User identity headers
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: K8s API Request (HTTPS/6443)<br/>User token (forwarded)
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: K8s API Response
    Dashboard-->>KRP: JSON Response
    KRP-->>Gateway: Response (HTTPS)
    Gateway-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Kubernetes Watch (WebSocket)
    Browser->>Gateway: WS Upgrade /wss/k8s/* (WSS/443)<br/>K8s subprotocol auth
    Gateway->>KRP: WebSocket (WSS/8443)
    KRP->>Dashboard: WebSocket (WS/8080, localhost)
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: WebSocket Watch (WSS/6443)<br/>base64url.bearer.authorization.k8s.io
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: Watch Events (streaming)
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Real-time Resource Updates

    Note over Browser,ModelRegUI: Flow 4: Module Federation (Model Registry UI)
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /_mf/modelRegistry/* (HTTPS/443)
    Gateway->>KRP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRP->>Dashboard: Forward (HTTP/8080)
    Dashboard->>ModelRegUI: Proxy (HTTPS/8043)<br/>User token header
    ModelRegUI-->>Dashboard: Federated JS Module
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Module Assets

    Note over Browser,GenAIUI: Flow 5: Module Federation (Gen AI UI)
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /_mf/genAi/* (HTTPS/443)
    Gateway->>KRP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRP->>Dashboard: Forward (HTTP/8080)
    Dashboard->>GenAIUI: Proxy (HTTPS/8143)<br/>User token header
    GenAIUI-->>Dashboard: Federated JS Module
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Module Assets

    Note over Dashboard,Prometheus: Flow 6: Prometheus Metrics Query
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/prometheus (HTTPS/443)
    Gateway->>KRP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRP->>Dashboard: Forward (HTTP/8080)
    Dashboard->>Prometheus: Metrics Query (HTTPS/9090)<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Prometheus-->>Dashboard: Metrics Data
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Metrics Response
